OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalians told to turn      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthermostats down           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Central heating will be restricted in  
OL,6, Italy this winter, as it becomes the   
OL,7, latest country to take action on       
OL,8, European gas supply shortages sparked  
OL,9, by Russia's invasion of Ukraine.       
OL,11,FUnder a new government decree,         
OL,12,Fbuildings will face an extra fifteen   
OL,13,Fdays without central heating.          
OL,15,FItalians will also be told to turn     
OL,16,Ftheir heating down by one degree, and  
OL,17,Foff for an extra hour a day.           
OL,19,FSome buildings will be exempt,         
OL,20,Fincluding nurseries and hospitals.     
